Description.Name: Misjump Moderate Repairs Completed
Description.Details:
Darius approaches you on the bridge, "Commander, I have been informed that all repairs to our drives have been completed and we are now back to 100% efficiency."

You nod, "Thank you, Darius."

Sumire, standing over by the Kerby-Fucheatah Console, grabs your attention, "Commander, do you want to activate the KF Console?

Description.Name: Keep KF Console Inactive
Description.Details: KF Console is INACTIVE

Description.Name: Keep KF Console Inactive
Description.Details:
You ponder her query for a few minutes before responding, "Leave the KF Console inactive for now and we will continue using normal travel for our next jump."

<color=#FFA500> The KF Console is currently</color><color=#FF0000> INACTIVE.</color>

Description.Name: Activate KF Console
Description.Details: KF Console is INACTIVE

Description.Name: Activate KF Console
Description.Details: You ponder her query for a few minutes before responding, "Set the KF Console to ACTIVE and we will use a Pirate Point for our next jump." The KF Console is now ACTIVE.
